---
title: Smart Slaw Salad and Turkey Meatballs with Peanut Dressing
description: This wholesome salad is bursting with fusion flavour, and even better: it comes together in no time! Fresh cucumbers and crispy, crunchy slaw are tossed together, then topped with succulent Thai-spiced meatballs and a drizzle of rich, creamy peanut-sesame dressing for a perfectly balanced bowl.

